  Requirements: 
    PHP3 3.0.8+ (100% PHP4-ready !)
    MySQL
                
  Summary:
    phpAds is a banner management and tracking system written in PHP3.
    Currently it can
    - manage multiple banners (any size) per client
    - view daily, overall and summary statistics
    - send statistics to clients via email
    - use HTML, GIF, JPEG and PNG-banners
    - show random, pre-defined or HTML/image banners
    - supports multiple keywords for groups of banners
    - supports conditional keywords
    - activate and deactivate single banners
    - show banners based on filters: user-agent, day-of-week, IP masks, domain, source page
    - Perform banner weighing
    - Target banner clicks to frames
    - Use random or sequential banner retrieval
  
  Download:
    You can get the newest version at http://www.sourceforge.net/projects/phpAdsNew/.

